{"tid":1460152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"給冷氣軍師的意見","createTime":"2019-08-13T01:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T02:33:44.000Z","uid":268983,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ca9f4e07296e8d46432818ea982a67035d3bf5d8","tid":1460152,"uid":268983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:32:26.000Z","msg":"收到消息今日機埸繼續有集會，唔該各位<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>不在現場無資格出聲</strong></span>, 特別係叫人去留。<br />\n2. 唔係自己一手料唔好放。<br />\n3. 未fact check(要有佐證)或無能力fc的料唔好放， <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>寧慢物錯</strong></span>，分享錯誤消息會害死人。<br />\n4. 傳聞唔好放，多數係假。<br />\n5. 過時 (超過一小時) 的料唔好再放。<br />\n6. 世上有其它媒體或機構幫手把把關先至放料，你的二手料多你一個唔多，少你一個可以幫到別人多一個收到正確資訊的機會。"},{"pid":"7ee449c7ba6fa66324bdbd79df4021721dee2f4a","tid":1460152,"uid":85451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:33:47.000Z","msg":"廣州獨立 福建獨立 北京獨立<br />\n四川獨立"},{"pid":"5ba1d78289fe9ca620b26fe761e5a3cc783d6152","tid":1460152,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:40:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0134529a682bb3213be782f5f934ec7ec3bdb7e4","tid":1460152,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:41:26.000Z","msg":"第1點已經唔同意<br />\n好多時候，現場網絡比較差，唔知外邊咩事"},{"pid":"5419a6198276d25b87d3849a50aa9f49c056bd35","tid":1460152,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:42:58.000Z","msg":"FACT CHECK好重要<br />\n亦係外圍可以幫機場做嘅事"},{"pid":"98a6c83d40e3b2225724a03cb52409c67c861d1e","tid":1460152,"uid":268983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0134529a682bb3213be782f5f934ec7ec3bdb7e4","tid":1460152,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T01:41:26.000Z","msg":"第1點已經唔同意<br />\n好多時候，現場網絡比較差，唔知外邊咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:33:44.000Z","msg":"相信前線的巴絲"}]}